videos.description: Xavier Johnson leaps for a one-yard touchdown to put South Alabama on the board.
videos.headline: Johnson hurdles into the end zone

videos.description: Cole Garvin's pass is intercepted by Troy's Jamal Stadom.
videos.headline: Stadom picks off Garvin

videos.description: Brandon Silvers' pass is tipped and intercepted by Jeremy Reaves on the South Alabama 3-yard line.
videos.headline: Reaves intercepts Troy on the 3-yard line

videos.description: Jordan Chunn is tackled in the end zone by Khalil McDonald to extend the Jaguars lead.
videos.headline: McDonald's tackle leads to a South Alabama safety

videos.description: Troy's Marcus Jones fumbles on the punt return at the 50-yard line and is recovered by South Alabama's Andrew Zink.
videos.headline: South Alabama recovers fumbled punt return

videos.description: Brandon Silvers runs for a one-yard touchdown in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Silvers sneaks into the end zone to put Troy on the board
